ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This software is the "Animal Vocalization Analysis Framework"
for cross-species communication research using the Universal Rosetta Stone
methodology.

Author: Sheel Morjaria (sheelmorjaria@gmail.com)

Citation:
Morjaria, S. (2025). Animal Vocalization Analysis Framework: Universal
Rosetta Stone Methodology for Cross-Species Communication Research.
Creative Commons BY-ND 4.0.

For more information about the research project, contact:
Sheel Morjaria (sheelmorjaria@gmail.com)

