COMPONENT LICENSES:

This framework includes the following components:

1. Technical Architecture (Rust Execution Layer)
   - Location: technical_architecture/
   - License: CC BY-ND 4.0 International
   - 415 tests passing
   - 21 source modules

2. Real-time Processing (Python Logic Layer)
   - Location: realtime/
   - License: CC BY-ND 4.0 International
   - Cognitive intelligence and decision making

3. Query Interface
   - Location: query_interface/
   - License: CC BY-ND 4.0 International
   - High-performance vocalization queries

4. Semiotic Engine
   - Location: semiotics/
   - License: CC BY-ND 4.0 International
   - Cognitive analysis capabilities

5. Synthesis Modules
   - Location: synthesis/
   - License: CC BY-ND 4.0 International
   - Audio synthesis engines

6. Data Models & Import
   - Location: data_models.py, data_import/
   - License: CC BY-ND 4.0 International
   - Cross-species data structures

All components are collectively licensed under CC BY-ND 4.0 International.

